snippet.textDisplay: Diana died because she decided that she would get into a car with a drunk driver, despite being advised against it. She also used the media when it suited her, like Meghan. We have enough problems with Ghastly Prince Andrew and his dodgy connections, without having to deal with a spoiled Prince and his fame crazy wife. In any event, if Harry and Megan believe they will have a more peaceful life now, they are very mistaken, if anything the press will be even more interested.
